  "text": "In regard to the potential role of post-ablation LGE CMR Hunter et al. have recently concluded that LGE CMR is not yet sufficiently accurate to reliably assess post-ablation lesion distribution. [CITATION_1] Moreover, LGE imaging does not seem to provide accurate information on the location of pulmonary veins reconnection sites in patients undergoing repeat ablation for AF. [CITATION_2] ",
